From 4f000871a51141c37d03f07addb5ad78cf0fc11e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 17:08:31 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Exp 7: Browse chrome key allowlist for TermSurf

When browse-forwardable, host-steal only allowlisted chrome
bindings (splits/tabs/zoom/quit); else bulk-forward to webview.
Zig classify + unit tests; AppKit preflight before forward.
